<dd><i>"Ancient" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Ancient_(disambiguation)" title="Ancient (disambiguation)">Ancient (disambiguation)</a>. The times before <a href="/wiki/Writing" title="Writing">writing</a> belong either to <a href="/wiki/Protohistory" title="Protohistory">protohistory</a> or to <a href="/wiki/Prehistory" title="Prehistory">prehistory</a>.</i></dd>
</dl>
