World in 100.</div>
</div>
</div>
<ul>
<li>117: Roman Empire at largest extent under <a href="/wiki/Trajan" title="Trajan">Emperor Trajan</a></li>
<li>192: <a href="/wiki/Kingdom_of_Champa" title="Kingdom of Champa" class="mw-redirect">Kingdom of Champa</a> in <a href="/wiki/Tay_Nguyen" title="Tay Nguyen" class="mw-redirect">Central Việt Nam</a></li>
</ul>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:224px;"><a href="/wiki/File:East-Hem_200ad.jpg" class="image" title="Eastern Hemisphere in 200 AD."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c4/East-Hem_200ad.jpg/222px-East-Hem_200ad.jpg" width="222" height="130" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
