<a href="/wiki/Khafre%27s_Pyramid" title="Khafre's Pyramid" class="mw-redirect">Khafre's Pyramid</a> (<a href="/wiki/Fourth_dynasty_of_Egypt" title="Fourth dynasty of Egypt" class="mw-redirect">4th dynasty</a>) and <a href="/wiki/Great_Sphinx_of_Giza" title="Great Sphinx of Giza">Great Sphinx of Giza</a> (c.2500 BC or perhaps earlier)</div>
